## Removing Columns

### Remove Single Column

```ruby
class RemoveBodyFromArticles < ActiveRecord::Migration[8.0]
  def change
    remove_column :articles, :body, :text
    # Include type for reversibility
  end
end
```

### Remove Multiple Columns

```ruby
class RemoveDetailsFromArticles < ActiveRecord::Migration[8.0]
  def change
    remove_column :articles, :excerpt, :text
    remove_column :articles, :subtitle, :string
  end
end
```

### Remove Reference

```ruby
class RemoveCategoryFromArticles < ActiveRecord::Migration[8.0]
  def change
    remove_reference :articles, :category, foreign_key: true
  end
end
```

